{"tid":2085238,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人要進步！","createTime":"2020-06-29T18:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T19:50:57.000Z","uid":229954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6507e5882edf2784f2e8bc6e727e17f23a1941cb","tid":2085238,"uid":229954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:25:19.000Z","msg":"你以為我講啲乜進步？<br />\n我講梗既係香港人個人既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">心態</span></span>&amp;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">自我思考</span></span>要進步吖！<br />\n都過咗成年喇 點解仲會有人問71究竟出唔出好？<br />\n重點係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> [問人]</span></span>！<br />\n識唔識得有返套自己既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">獨立思考</span></span>。<br />\n我自己唔會叫人一定要出吖果啲，<br />\n因為覺得咁做係情緒勒索<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一年lu，香港人應該都識長大架喇，<br />\n經過咁多事件。關於送頭圍捕大家都有一定意識既我諗。<br />\n所以你問71出定唔出，<br />\n其實真係好睇自己個人既心點諗<br />\n因為每件事 都會有<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">好</span></span></strong>有<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">壞</span></span></strong> 一定有兩面去睇既 同咪一定會有矛盾既位。<br />\n係睇你自己偏向於邊一方面多啲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我舉個例吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到咗今時今日 仲有個討論位既就係勇武抗爭方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有一派既人會話：放棄啦 根本都唔得，都試咗咁多次啦，我哋有邊次係得既姐？咁多次既硬碰硬，最後結果呢？咪又係攞自己黎博飛，分分鐘仲已經變咗condom喇。傷既又係自己，又要攰。<br />\n<br />\n但同時一定又會有一派既人出黎反駁上面既果一派人講既野。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢哋會話：抗爭唔係就係一定會流血架咩，冇流血既點叫革命？如果個個人都只係嗌口號，咁有咩用？如果呢一刻咁多人退，咁呢場革命就注定失敗啦。同時亦都係因為咁多人都退，留返係前既就得好少，所以先變成真正既condom吖！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你睇！呢個就係我講既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">矛盾位</span></span>。<br />\n亦都係我哋香港人要思考既野。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要思考既唔淨只係抗爭既模式，<br />\n而係去思考每做一件事既時候，<br />\n自己個心係點諗，唔應該盲目去跟風。<br />\n<br />\n香港人俾啲自我獨行思考好唔好！<br />\n將來嘅嘢冇人會知，忠於自己既心，做啲自己唔會後悔嘅事我覺得就可以了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6140f763c9bf92687f8415c2a20003459c78e889","tid":2085238,"uid":118217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"對自己負責"},{"pid":"2f2fe31e7390156e7b4e546c116133385f4a208a","tid":2085238,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"一屌某條友好多人唔會自己諗吓先就跟風屌埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae27e8fcb30a3676e6cfc2e66e5fc3328d535da","tid":2085238,"uid":229954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f2fe31e7390156e7b4e546c116133385f4a208a","tid":2085238,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"一屌某條友好多人唔會自己諗吓先就跟風屌埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:30:52.000Z","msg":"呢啲都係我呢一年從運動所學到既野，曾經都一味識得沖沖沖。人哋up乜我就勁by佢哋個講法。原全唔識兩方面去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb5d49dbd3237e393f12abcd5ea56ac980b4753","tid":2085238,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f2fe31e7390156e7b4e546c116133385f4a208a","tid":2085238,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"一屌某條友好多人唔會自己諗吓先就跟風屌埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住就會屈毛"},{"pid":"66d01f991927393d9662c0ad3d2d45932f905d22","tid":2085238,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:50:57.000Z","msg":"一人一post推71<br />\n<span style=\"font-s